## 🔒 Enterprise Safety Features

### **Automatic Safeguards**
- ✅ **Complete backup** before any changes (timestamped in `legacy/migration-archives/`)
- ✅ **File integrity hashes** for verification (SHA256)
- ✅ **Build validation** (.NET, NPM, Docker automatic testing)
- ✅ **Rollback capability** (automatic on validation failure)
- ✅ **Audit trails** (complete logs in `agents/workspace/logs/`)
- ✅ **Configuration archiving** (successful configs saved for reference)

### **Zero Data Loss Policy**
- ✅ **Never delete without archiving** first
- ✅ **Multiple backup layers** (pre-migration + execution archives)
- ✅ **Metadata preservation** (original paths, timestamps, reasons)
- ✅ **Recovery procedures** documented and automated

